                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-169-victim1591 t18201206-169-viclabel1008"></join>, in <placeName id="t18201206-169-crimeloc1009">Queen-street, Commercial-road</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18201206-169-crimeloc1009" type="placeName" value="Queen-street, Commercial-road"></interp>
                  <interp inst="t18201206-169-crimeloc1009" type="type" value="crimeLocation"></interp>
                  <join result="offencePlace" targOrder="Y" targets="t18201206-169-off1006 t18201206-169-crimeloc1009"></join>. On the 2d of December, about ten o'clock I called my boy in and in a few minutes after I heard a noise, went out and missed a cheese from near the door. I heard a cry of Stop thief! and saw Porter rolling the cheese to the door. In a few minutes the prisoner was brought back.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18201206-169-person1593">
                  BENJAMIN 
                  PORTER
               <interp inst="t18201206-169-person1593" type="surname" value="PORTER"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18201206-169-person1593" type="given" value="BENJAMIN"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18201206-169-person1593" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . On the 2d of December I saw the prisoner lurking about, and saw him take the cheese. I stopped him with it, and brought him back.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18201206-169-person1594">
                  WILLIAM 
                  CARTER
               <interp inst="t18201206-169-person1594" type="surname" value="CARTER"></interp>
